<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_603" id="300v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_603_r1l14"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıenharte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Graue<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü Caſtell </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_603_r1l15">Gnedıger
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vvir ſchicken cʒü
                                                eẅrn gnaden hannſen Göldlein
                                                  <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_603_r1l16">diener dem vvir beuolhen
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <del rend="strikethrough">ewrn fürſtenlıch </del>
<expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eẅrn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_603_r1l17">gnaden ʒu reden <add><ab facs="#facs_603_line_1592208415917_4511">als
                                                  </ab></add> von geleits wegen diſer meſſe etc vt
                                                  <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_603_r1l18"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Conrad Schencken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_603_r1l19"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_603" id="300v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lienharte<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>graue<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü Castell </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir schicken
                                                czü ewrn gnaden Hannsen Göldlein,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, dem wir
                                                bevolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrn gnaden zu
                                                reden <add>als</add> von geleits wegen diser messe
                                                etc. ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Conrad Schencken,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
